 1855 , but has not been much used since the early decades of the 20th century."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Maud FitzRichard was born in 1175, in Woodplumpton, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom, her father, Richard FitzRoger of Woodplumpton, was 47 and her mother, Margery de Banastre, was 25. She married Robert de Stockport in 1194, in Stockport, Cheshire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter. She died in 1206, in Stockport, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 31."},"et":{"1175–1206":"1175–1206","1170–1206":"1170–1206","1192–1237":"1192–1237","1199–1249":"1199–1249","1129–1201":"1129–1201","1150–1206":"1150–1206","1175":"1175","1194":"1194","1183":"1183","1150":"1150","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","1206":"1206","1129":"1129","1249":"1249","1237":"1237","1201":"1201","1199":"1199","Bef 1192":"enne 1192","Stockport, Cheshire, England":"Stockport, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Woodplumpton, Preston, Lancashire, England":"Woodplumpton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Woodplumpton, Lancashire, England":"Woodplumpton, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1175–1206":"1175–1206","1170–1206":"1170–1206","1192–1237":"1192–1237","1199–1249":"1199–1249","1129–1201":"1129–1201","1150–1206":"1150–1206","1175":"1175","1194":"1194","1183":"1183","1150":"1150","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","1206":"1206","1129":"1129","1249":"1249","1237":"1237","1201":"1201","1199":"1199","Bef 1192":"ennen vuotta 1192","Stockport, Cheshire, England":"Stockport, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Woodplumpton, Preston, Lancashire, England":"Woodplumpton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Woodplumpton, Lancashire, England":"Woodplumpton, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1175–1206":"1175–1206","1170–1206":"1170–1206","1192–1237":"1192–1237","1199–1249":"1199